The '''Book of Misfortune''' is one of the main [[spell book]]s for [[Hexes]].

==Spells==
{{spellbook|Book of Misfortune}}

== History ==
*Prior to [[0.18]], it was called Book of Hinderance and didn't contain [[Yara's Violent Unravelling]].
*Prior to [[0.17]], it contained [[Slow]] and [[Summon Mana Viper]].
*Prior to [[0.16]], it contained [[Leda's Liquefaction]] instead of [[Gell's Gravitas]].
